{"tid":29262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個見義勇為既經歷","createTime":"2016-12-08T12:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T14:59:07.000Z","uid":26115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"036e0c80687153207ae6ae945f5252f81457e974","tid":29262,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"小二果陣班入面有個智障既同學成日俾人蝦，有一日小息佢俾人打，唔知咩事我竟然走左埋去阻止，之後仲教個智障同學，以後你俾人打，記得要還手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢俾人蝦，真係好狠咁還拖，仲要同老師講話係我教佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我俾人的左上校長室話要記過，校長好嬲咁問我做咩要教個同學打人，我喊哂咁講:「因為我唔想佢俾人蝦。」<br />\n<br />\n之後校長講左句以後唔好就放左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從此之後果個智障同學就冇俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a953ae0b60c3b5f3990991631d387625b93f23b","tid":29262,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵叫班撚人「行撚入啲」算唔算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2898a3e24a9f0cd9c63fa06c83797573c7864566","tid":29262,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ac6a736204bebf447b2ad2186f74f92529f5f6","tid":29262,"uid":3643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"樓主呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe6bee2bec58fbbf9bf67bf997aa529e86d271b","tid":29262,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似日本動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b6a9c16cc18a6dcb15ca